1. *Traga* se za odgovorima. (He/She is searching for answers.)
2. Ona je *tragala* po knjigama. (She was looking through the books.)
3. *Tragovi* su je doveli do istine. (The traces led her to the truth.)
4. Oni su *tragali* po svetu. (They were searching through the world.)
5. Policija je *tragala* za ukradenim slikama. (The police were searching for the stolen pictures.)
6. Ona je *tragala* za odgovorom. (She was looking for an answer.)